injuries.longComment: Poeltl logged 24 minutes in Friday's contest, posting 10 points (5-15 FG), 10 rebounds, two steals, two blocks and one assist. The big man's next opportunity to suit up will come in Wednesday's regular-season opener against the Hawks.
injuries.shortComment: Poeltl won't return to Friday's preseason game against the Nets due to stiffness in his lower back, Kayla Grey of TSN reports.

injuries.longComment: Murray-Boyles will end up on the shelf to finish Toronto's preseason. The rookie first-rounder appears to be a real question mark for Wednesday's season opener in Atlanta.
injuries.shortComment: Murray-Boyles (elbow) has been ruled out for Friday's preseason game against the Nets, Michael Grange of Sportsnet.ca reports.
